OL,3,CMan stabbed to death at Primrose Hill
OL,4,Cviewpoint
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after a 21-year-old man was
OL,8,Fstabbed to death at Primrose Hill's
OL,9,Fviewpoint.
OL,11,FThe Metropolitan Police said officers
OL,12,Fwere called at 6.41pm on Tuesday to
OL,13,Freports of a fight at the popular
OL,14,Fnorth London park, which boasts
OL,15,Fpanoramic views of the capital.
OL,17,FOfficers attended alongside the London
OL,18,FAmbulance Service, who treated a 21-
OL,19,Fyear-old man at the scene for stab
OL,20,Fwounds.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
