OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775639132
OL,3,CMan stabbed to death at Primrose Hill
OL,4,Cviewpoint
OL,6,FDespite the efforts of paramedics, he
OL,7,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,9,FAnother man, believed to be in his
OL,10,F20s, was found by police nearby on
OL,11,FRegent's Park Road with stab wounds.
OL,13,FHe was taken to hospital by paramedics
OL,14,Fand his injuries are not believed to
OL,15,Fbe life-threatening or life-changing.
OL,17,FNo arrests have been made yet and a
OL,18,Fcrime scene remained in place on
OL,19,FTuesday evening.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
