FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775639132
OL,3,CMan stabbed to death at Primrose Hill
OL,4,Cviewpoint
OL,6,FLast year, a teenager was locked up
OL,7,Ffor at least 16 years for fatally
OL,8,Fstabbing a 16-year-old boy in the neck
OL,9,Fat a New Year's Eve fireworks event at
OL,10,FPrimrose Hill on December 31 2023.
OL,12,FSuperintendent Matt Cox said: "This is
OL,13,Fan utterly tragic incident and our
OL,14,Fthoughts remain with the man's family
OL,15,Fand loved ones.
OL,17,F"I would like to reassure the local
OL,18,Fcommunity that the investigation is
OL,19,Funfolding at pace and an increased
OL,20,Fpolice presence will remain in the
OL,21,Farea while we carry out inquiries.
OL,26,@tD@_OUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
