OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775639132
OL,3,CMan stabbed to death at Primrose Hill
OL,4,Cviewpoint
OL,6,F"I would appeal for anyone who was in
OL,7,Fthe area at the time and has any
OL,8,Finformation that could help my
OL,9,Fofficers to come forward."
OL,11,FAnyone with information that may
OL,12,Fassist police is asked to call 101,
OL,13,Fquoting CAD 6448/07Apr or contact
OL,14,FCrimestoppers anonymously on 0800 555
OL,15,F111.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
